platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: OK Golf is as stress-free as a golf game gets. We love the cool, crisp lines of the striking polygonal courses, and the one-touch controls are easy to get a grip on. When we do slice one out of bounds, we just pretend we were aiming for one of the many off-course secret bonus holes.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: The joy of sinking a perfect shot without sunburns or squawking seagulls.
日焼けやカモメに悩まされることなく、最高のショットをカップに沈めよう。
Les joies du golf sans les coups de soleil.
